Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.32,0:38:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再也无法盼望夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.83,0:38:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,心如刀绞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.87,0:38:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.58,0:38:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.00,0:38:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,留在手中的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.21,0:38:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和夏天的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.00,0:38:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,都将永远伴随着我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.81,0:38:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来  走吧
